{"tid":1764273,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"老人家忽然有急性老人痴呆，有冇可靠老人定位器介紹？","createTime":"2019-12-01T03:55:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-13T17:00:06.000Z","uid":68776,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"def9c28576d2e0ba8a8df1bc5006e696f49bb293","tid":1764273,"uid":68776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T03:55:25.000Z","msg":"尋日第一次唔見，有老人手機但係佢講唔到自己系邊。最後要途人協助先搵到佢。<br />\n<br />\n想搵啲輕便既畀佢佩戴，可以隨時知佢系邊得黎佢又肯帶。<br />\n<br />\n希望有使用過既朋友介紹。"},{"pid":"ff2ce72d46b949c3ef039c6e5eb18065aacec5b4","tid":1764273,"uid":307619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T03:57:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.schsa.org.hk/tc/services/safe_services/addvalue/eseefind/index.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.schsa.org.hk%2Ftc%2Fservices%2Fsafe_services%2Faddvalue%2Feseefind%2Findex.html&d=HsMqQMGMM0KOGi%2FJd%2BN0B5ggdM0W6%2BkgeusliPwa7Y4%3D&h=0c6f6d68\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.schsa.org.hk/tc/services/safe_services/addvalue/eseefind/index.html</a>"},{"pid":"72209fc2cb8bc5f7047f4b2af00e77e0752379ab","tid":1764273,"uid":53122,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T03:57:47.000Z","msg":"買隻兒童gps手錶<br />\n幾百蚊靚靚地"},{"pid":"27d72f28c92490ece5e84e01522a672512ac6dfe","tid":1764273,"uid":1550,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T03:59:06.000Z","msg":"唔應該比佢一個人出去"},{"pid":"5f10cec35ea81b5ebcfda71dd21df0c22eaaf979","tid":1764273,"uid":16654,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T03:59:13.000Z","msg":"入咗醫院檢查未<br />\n醫生確認咗係腦退化?"},{"pid":"8f67c93ebb1cf0c31af85bbf43189b7a17448bda","tid":1764273,"uid":221055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ff2ce72d46b949c3ef039c6e5eb18065aacec5b4","tid":1764273,"uid":307619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T03:57:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.schsa.org.hk/tc/services/safe_services/addvalue/eseefind/index.h